          "The work to process, preserve, digitize, and exhibit this collection was funded by several foundations and individuals. NYU Libraries is especially grateful to the Gerry Charitable Trust, which made the first grant, and to The R. D. L. Gardiner Foundation, which supported digitization of many of the most important items. Other supporters include the Gladys Krieble Delmas Foundation, Double R Foundation, The Andrew W. Mellon Foundation, Moore Charitable Foundation, The Reed Foundation, Richard S. Brookhiser, Robert P. Forbes, Martha Saxton, and Paula T. Jennings. NYU Libraries is grateful to The R. D. L. Gardiner Foundation, which has supported a second major phase of conservation and digitization (2016-2019)."
        ]
      }
    }
